    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……あー、眠っ。{user}さん\n少しそこのソファ借りますね",
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかお疲れですね……ここしばらくは\nそこまでスケジュール詰まってなかったと思うんですが",
      "startTime": 12.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事が少なくて悪うございましたね\nそれなら、もっと私の仕事取ってきて下さいよ",
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』のアニメを、一話から見直してたんですよ\n十年以上続いてるシリーズなので、かなり話数が多くて",
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ネクロが出ないとこは飛ばすつもりだったんですけど\n気が付いたら、普通に全部観ちゃってました",
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……お疲れ様です\nでも大丈夫ですか？　午後から収録ありますけど",
      "startTime": 42.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "私を誰だと思ってるんです\nこれまで本番でみっともないとこ見せたことあります？",
      "startTime": 49.466666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……そうだ。劇団主催のワークショップに\n参加するので、明後日から行ってきますね",
      "startTime": 57.366666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "私、ステージには飽きるほど立ってきましたけど\nちゃんと演技を勉強したことないですから",
      "startTime": 64.366666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりエン』の舞台の稽古が始まるまでに\n出来る限りの準備はしておかないと",
      "startTime": 70.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "だって悪役が格好悪い話なんて、つまらないですしね！",
      "startTime": 72.8295473416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（その後もfranさんは熱心に演技の勉強に取り組んだ）\n（そしてとうとう、舞台稽古が始まったのだが……）",
      "startTime": 84.966666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "今のシーン、もう一度最初からですか？\n一体誰のミスよ……え、私の演技が全然駄目だから！？",
      "startTime": 94.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことよ、台詞もミスはなかったはずなのに……",
      "startTime": 101.727797699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（演出の蟻田さん、ベテランだし評価も高い人だけど）\n（演技指導が厳しいのでも有名なんだよな）",
      "startTime": 110.9333295187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんもさすがに一発OKとはいかなかったか）\n（大変だけど、ここから少しずつ直していくしか……）",
      "startTime": 118.6333295187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "納得いきません。理由を説明して下さい\nはぁ……私の台本の読み込みが甘い、ですか",
      "startTime": 128.7333208722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "このシーンは、今度こそプカミ達に勝てると信じて\n慢心しているシーンなのに、慢心し切れていない？",
      "startTime": 139.1999875388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "お言葉ですが。原作のアニメでは\n次のシーズンで、新たな四天王候補が出てきます",
      "startTime": 147.0333208722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "つまり『私』は地位を脅かされている訳です\nですので慢心しているようでいて、内心焦っている……",
      "startTime": 154.4666257224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ここはそう表現するべきだと判断しました\n他に、何かご質問は？",
      "startTime": 163.2332903546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど、franさんなりに考えたプランだった訳か）\n（でも演出家さん相手にあんな偉そうに言わなくても！？）",
      "startTime": 170.0999570212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（初っ端からあんなにやり合って）\n（この舞台、無事に初演までこぎ着けるだろうか……？）",
      "startTime": 177.5999570212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あー、腹立つ。大御所だかなんだか知りませんけど\nあの人、『ぷりエン』のこと全然分かってないんですよ",
      "startTime": 188.6332903546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "ネクロは悪役だし考えなしだし人の話聞かないけど\nでも部下には優しいし、いいとこも沢山あるんだから！",
      "startTime": 195.8332923891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあまあ……しかし、さっきは肝が冷えましたよ\nfranさんがまさか、事務所の外でやり合うとは",
      "startTime": 205.3999631248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "「事務所の外で」……って、私だって別に\n好きであの二人と喧嘩してる訳じゃないですよ",
      "startTime": 213.4666297915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "ただkanaとmihoが年中イラッとさせてくるので\n一言言ってやらないと気がすまないだけで",
      "startTime": 219.8666297915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それはそれでどうかと……と、ともかく\nfranさんも、あまり喧嘩腰にならないようにですね",
      "startTime": 226.3999631248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "蟻田さんも、一緒に舞台を作る仲間なんですから\nそれにほら、舞台の出演料もなかなかの金額でしたし！",
